      "content": "i understand but i've heard that sometimes these things are just viral and they go away without any meds. if i use the drops to keep it lubricated and maybe do some warm compresses, wouldn't that be a safe way to manage it at home for a bit? i really don't want to go to the doctor unless it gets way worse.",
